arne\", \"from\": 1396, \"to\": 1412}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Alongside euphoria, there was also relief when they crossed the line.\", \"from\": 1415, \"to\": 1484, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"euphoria\", \"from\": 1425, \"to\": 1433}, {\"ngram\": \"relief\", \"from\": 1450, \"to\": 1456}, {\"ngram\": \"the line\", \"from\": 1475, \"to\": 1483}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Grant and Craig were supposedly the banker of the Games and though it was not comfortable, they rarely looked troubled.\", \"from\": 1485, \"to\": 1604, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1495, \"end\": 1500, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Craig_Dean\", \"score\": 0.9999956677896242, \"rank\": 4.293561957003369e-06, \"text\": \"Craig\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Craig_Dean\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Craig_Dean\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Grant\", \"from\": 1485, \"to\": 1490}, {\"ngram\": \"the banker\", \"from\": 1517, \"to\": 1527}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 1531, \"to\": 1540}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At least, that was, until the podium when the emotions all became too much.\", \"from\": 1606, \"to\": 1681, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the podium\", \"from\": 1632, \"to\": 1642}, {\"ngram\": \"the emotions\", \"from\": 1648, \"to\": 1660}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Ugly crying on international TV?\", \"from\": 1683, \"to\": 1716, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"international TV\", \"from\": 1699, \"to\": 1715}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Super,\\\" said Craig, whois one of over 1,000 elite athletes on UK Sport's National Lottery-funded World Class Programme, allowing them to train full time, have access to the world's best coaches and benefit from pioneering medical support - which has been vital on their pathway to theParis 2024Games.\", \"from\": 1717, \"to\": 2017, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1730, \"end\": 1735, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Craig_Dean\", \"score\": 0.9999956677896242, \"rank\": 4.293561957003369e-06, \"text\": \"Craig\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Craig_Dean\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Craig_Dean\"}, {\"begin\": 1779, \"end\": 1787, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UK_Sport\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"UK Sport\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UK_Sport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UK_Sport\"}, {\"begin\": 1779, \"end\": 1787, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UK_Sport\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"UK Sport\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UK_Sport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UK_Sport\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Super\", \"from\": 1717, \"to\": 1722}, {\"ngram\": \"whois\", \"from\": 1737, \"to\": 1742}, {\"ngram\": \"over 1,000 elite athletes\", \"from\": 1750, \"to\": 1775}, {\"ngram\": \"access\", \"from\": 1876, \"to\": 1882}, {\"ngram\": \"the world's best coaches\", \"from\": 1886, \"to\": 1910}, {\"ngram\": \"medical support\", \"from\": 1939, \"to\": 1954}, {\"ngram\": \"their pathway\", \"from\": 1981, \"to\": 1994}, {\"ngram\": \"theParis\", \"from\": 1998, \"to\": 2006}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Every time I thought about the moment, it has brought me to tears and so I had to try and not think about it for a very long time.\", \"from\": 2019, \"to\": 2150, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the moment\", \"from\": 2047, \"to\": 2057}, {\"ngram\": \"tears\", \"from\": 2080, \"to\": 2085}, {\"ngram\": \"a very long time\", \"from\": 2133, \"to\": 2149}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Was I surprised that was my emotion?\", \"from\": 2151, \"to\": 2187, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my emotion\", \"from\": 2176, \"to\": 2186}]}, {\"sentence\": \"No.\", \"from\": 2188, \"to\": 2191, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There was pressure but also confidence.\", \"from\": 2193, \"to\": 2233, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"pressure\", \"from\": 2204, \"to\": 2212}, {\"ngram\": \"confidence\", \"from\": 2222, \"to\": 2232}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We just had to go out and do something we have done multiple times before.\", \"from\": 2234, \"to\": 2308, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 2263, \"to\": 2272}, {\"ngram\": \"multiple times\", \"from\": 2286, \"to\": 2300}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We knew we did not have to pull something out of thin air, we just had to race the race plan that we have.\", \"from\": 2310, \"to\": 2417, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 2343, \"to\": 2352}, {\"ngram\": \"thin air\", \"from\": 2360, \"to\": 2368}, {\"ngram\": \"the race plan\", \"from\": 2390, \"to\": 2403}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It saw us over the line first.\", \"from\": 2418, \"to\": 2448, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 2425, \"to\": 2427}, {\"ngram\": \"the line\", \"from\": 2433, \"to\": 2441}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was a blur, to be honest, it was the quickest race of our lives.\\\"\", \"from\": 2450, \"to\": 2519, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a blur\", \"from\": 2458, \"to\": 2464}, {\"ngram\": \"the quickest race\", \"from\": 2487, \"to\": 2504}, {\"ngram\": \"our lives\", \"from\": 2508, \"to\": 2517}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Craig and Grant were happy to let Romania open up a small lead at 500m but as soon as they hit the throttle, the British pair were gone.\", \"from\": 2521, \"to\": 2657, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2521, \"end\": 2526, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Craig_Dean\", \"score\": 0.9999956677896242, \"rank\": 4.293561957003369e-06, \"text\": \"Craig\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Craig_Dean\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpe